* define RDEU specification with no errors
cap program drop MLdropout
program define MLdropout
  args lnf prob alphar var
  tempvar choice winpc winval outval
  tempvar adjprob alpha
  tempvar euIN euOUT euDiff euRatio 

generate double `alpha' =`alphar'
// generate double `var' = exp(`varr') + 1
  
qui {
* read in data
generate int `choice' = $ML_y1
generate double `winpc' = $ML_y2
generate double `winval' = $ML_y3
generate double `outval' = $ML_y4

// euIN


* generate the weighted probabilities
//generate double `adjprob' = (`winpc'^`prob')/(`winpc'^`prob' + (1-`winpc')^`prob')^(1/`prob')
generate double `adjprob' = `prob'

* Calculate utility values
generate double `euIN' = `adjprob'*((`winval')^(`alpha')) + `var'
generate double `euOUT' = 1*(`outval')^(`alpha')

generate double `euDiff' = `euIN' - `euOUT'

* likelihood
replace `lnf' = ln(normal( `euDiff')) if `choice'==0
replace `lnf' = ln(normal(-`euDiff')) if `choice'==1

sum `lnf' `euIN' `euOUT' `gamma' 

}
end


set more off

// only for setup, set to 1==1 to run
if ( 1==1 ) {

cd /Users/mas/Dropbox/OET
use "oetaug2010_pitstoplevel_v8.dta", clear

sort subjectid pitstopid

// list subjectid raceid pitstopid dropout

// create a proper dropout dummy, 0 = not yet droped out, 1 = drop out, . = prev drop out
gen dropoutD = .
replace dropoutD = 0 if pitstopnum == 1 & dropout == "false"
replace dropoutD = 1 if pitstopnum == 1 & dropout == "true"
replace dropoutD = 0 if pitstopnum == 2 & dropout == "false" & dropout[_n-1] == "false"
replace dropoutD = 1 if pitstopnum == 2 & dropout == "true" & dropout[_n-1] == "false"
replace dropoutD = 0 if pitstopnum == 3 & dropout == "false" & dropout[_n-1] == "false"
replace dropoutD = 1 if pitstopnum == 3 & dropout == "true" & dropout[_n-1] == "false"

drop if mi(dropoutD)
drop if winvalue == 0

gen pse = psexpectation/1000
}


// list dropoutD winpc winvalue dropoutvalue 

xi: ml model lf MLdropout (prob: dropoutD winpc winvalue dropoutvalue = winpc pse) (alpha:) (var: ) if pitstopnum > 1
ml search
ml maximize
